    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"110064\">Kenny Lau</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113489-new-members/topic/calc.20xy/near/525540478\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>i'm teaching you to basically think harder about what you are actually doing in each step of a pen-and-paper proof</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>My math background is computer science so I haven't done much pen and paper proofs and it was a long time ago. What I am trying to say is I don't know what the difference is between pen and paper proof and calc method.</p>",
