        "timestamp": 1750777863
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Sorry if my thought process isn't comprehensible <span aria-label=\"sweat smile\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f605\" role=\"img\" title=\"sweat smile\">:sweat_smile:</span></p>",
        "id": 525541468,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1750778060
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I really need to understand an algorithm for coming up with first step or I will have to keep asking questions like this :(</p>",
        "id": 525542311,
        "sender_full_name": "Răzvan Flavius Panda",
        "timestamp": 1750778321
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"816344\">@Aaron Liu</span> I tried to understand but I still don't know how you came up with <code>(y - 2) * (x + 5 - (x + 3)) / 2 + 2</code> as first step</p>",
        "id": 525542594,
        "sender_full_name": "Răzvan Flavius Panda",
        "timestamp": 1750778396
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The first step was coming up with the fact that I need <code>2 - (2 * x - y * x) / 2</code>, and then I worked backwards from there</p>",
        "id": 525542754,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1750778456
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>And how did you figure out you need <code>2 - (2 * x - y * x) / 2</code> and not <code>2 - (2 * x - y * x)</code> ?</p>",
        "id": 525543025,
        "sender_full_name": "Răzvan Flavius Panda",
        "timestamp": 1750778533
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Since <code>x = 2</code>, I can derive that <code>y = 2 - (2 * 2 - y * 2) / 2</code>, but I can't get <code>y = 2 - (2 * 2 - y * 2)</code></p>",
        "id": 525543222,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1750778598
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I see, that makes sense.</p>",
        "id": 525543504,
        "sender_full_name": "Răzvan Flavius Panda",
        "timestamp": 1750778691
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Ok, I managed to solve it reasoning backwards from <code>2 - (2 * x - y * x) / 2</code></p>",
        "id": 525545419,
        "sender_full_name": "Răzvan Flavius Panda",
        "timestamp": 1750779243
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>But I am not sure how much is thinking and how much rote memorization.</p>",
        "id": 525545513,
        "sender_full_name": "Răzvan Flavius Panda",
        "timestamp": 1750779266
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I thought I would have to ask a question for this one also but it turned out to be easy:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℚ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">4</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">calc</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">q</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ring</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h2</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">4</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ring</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 525548989,
        "sender_full_name": "Răzvan Flavius Panda",
        "timestamp": 1750780247
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Once someone else asked how the sum of squares could be negative</p>",
        "id": 525549217,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1750780327
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"816344\">@Aaron Liu</span> One last question, is there an algorithm on how you figured out to start with <code>y = 2 - (2 * 2 - y * 2) / 2</code>. I understood the /2 part just not how to get at that step.</p>",
        "id": 525549389,
        "sender_full_name": "Răzvan Flavius Panda",
