    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"816344\">Aaron Liu</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113489-new-members/topic/calc.20xy/near/525549217\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Once someone else asked how the sum of squares could be negative</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Complex numbers I'm guessing.</p>",
